title: Watch video: The Rock calls CM Punk after WWE Raw ends
text:
The Rock 
Former WWE superstar The Rock appeared on the latest episode of WWE Raw, in order to shoot for upcoming Hollywood film 'Fighting with My Family', which is a biopic based on WWE female wrestler Paige.
The Hollywood star entered the ring after WWE Raw ended so as to begin shooting a sequence for the film. The fans then began chating another wrestler's name - CM Punk.

The Rock calls CM Punk. Pic Courtesy/ YouTube 
An amused Dwayne Johnson aka The Rock then decided to give CM Punk a call. On receiving no answer, The Rock then sent a voicemail to CM Punk. Check out the full video below that was posted on Twitter.
. @TheRock leaves @CMPunk a voicemail! #WWE pic.twitter.com/twHtDFqC5z 
â€” NoDQ.com - WWE News (@nodqdotcom) February 21, 2017 The Rock won the WWE title from CM Punk at Royal Rumble in 2013, ending his record world title reign of 434 days. The Rock also awaits the release of his two Hollywood projects - -The Fate of the Furious' and 'Baywatch'.
